<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188975>
    dc:description "FIGURES 54 – 58. Cuticular structure of females Cunaxa spp. nov.: Cunaxa gordeevae sp. nov. (54); Cunaxa maculate sp. nov. (55, 56); Cunaxa papuliphora sp. nov. (57); Cunaxa violaphila sp. nov. (58)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188975/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188964>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Cunaxa gordeevae sp. nov., female. Palp (1); proximal part of gnathosoma, dorsolateral aspect (2); hypognathum (3); idiosomal dorsum (4); idiosomal venter (5). Scale-bar: 1 – 3, 50 μm; 4, 5, 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188964/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188965>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 9. Cunaxa gordeevae sp. nov., female. Genu, tibia and proximal part of tarsus of: leg I (6), leg II (7); genu and tibia of: leg III (8), leg IV (9). Scale-bar— 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188965/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

